reviewText:
if you want to feel uplifted, transcended to a higher place, this will do it!

true talent. you simply have to see this.

it is so moving when artists who have been traveling in certain circles decide to go indie and suddenly, you see the full strength of their creativity over-flow and dazzle.

i enjoy indie spirits and good talent- this has it all. and it's good for you too, cuz you're gonna feel so much better about the world:-)

This is fullfillment.....this  is creativity that has been passed on with the blessings of the ancestors.
 Baba Issa has resided in the rarified air for many moons and suns.....toiled in the vineyards.
 The fullfillment of prayer.
 in peace............
